    "These models can analyze sensor data and provide repair or replacement recommendations.",
    "Predictive maintenance models can be integrated with electronic health records to view medical device performance and patient outcomes comprehensively.",
    "This can help healthcare providers make informed medical device management and patient care decisions.",
    "These are just some of the future works and ideas that can be explored in the predictive maintenance of medical devices using DL and IoT-based bio-and medical informatics.",
